---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import "./../css/index.css"
---
<Layout
    title="Custom Website Development | Sharguidev"
    description="Professional web development services for small businesses and startups. Fast, responsive, and SEO-friendly websites."
    canonical="https://sharguidev.com/FAQs"
>
    <h2 style="display: flex; justify-content:center; align-items: center; margin-top: 5%;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div id="faqservices" class="container-FAQservices mt-5">
            <div class="accordion" id="faq-section">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                    What is included in each package?
                </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faq-section" id="accordionItem">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Each package includes specific services tailored to your needs. For example, the UX/UI package includes high-quality design, a color palette of your preference and 2 extra revisions. Check the package details to find the best fit for your project.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                    How do I know which package is right for me?
                </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section" >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    If you're unsure, consider the complexity of your project. If you only need a design, the UX/UI package is ideal. If you need a complete website, a Full Stack package would be better. Feel free to contact me for guidance.
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#customize" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                    Can I customize my package?
                </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="customize" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Yes! If none of the packages fit your exact needs, we can discuss a custom solution tailored to your requirements.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="mt-3 dynamic-text">Process & Revisions</h3>
            <div class="accordion-item mt-3">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#process" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        How does the development process work?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="process" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Once you choose a package, we will discuss your requirements, design preferences, goals, payments dates and methods. I will then start working on your project and provide updates throughout the process.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#Revisions" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        How many revisions do I get?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="Revisions" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Each package includes two extra revisions. If you need more, additional revisions can be arranged for an extra fee.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="mt-3 dynamic-text">Payments & Timeline</h3>
            <div class="accordion-item mt-3">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#payments" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                       What payments methods do you accept?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="payments" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        I accept payments via PayPal, Bank Transfer (BAC, Banco Nacional, Grupo Mutual).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#deposit" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Do I need to pay upfront?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="deposit" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Yes, a deposit of the 15% is required to start the project, and the remaining balance is due upon completed phases.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#time" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        How long does it takes to complete a project?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="time" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        The timeline depends on the complexity of the project. A basic UX/UI design may take a few days 3 maximum, while a full-stack project can take a few weeks or few months. We will agree on a timeline before starting.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 dynamic-text">Technical Questions</h3>
            <div class="accordion-item mt-3">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#responsive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                       Will my website be mobile-friendly?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="responsive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Yes! All designs and developments are fully responsive, ensuring they work well on all devices.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#support" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Do you provide ongoing support after the project is completed?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="support" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Yes, I do offer post-launch support with troubleshooting for free but if you need maintanance, new features or updates of colors or the position of anything would be charged wit an extra fee.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#edit" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Will I be able to edit my website after it's completed?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="edit" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq-section">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Yes and No! If you want me to edit something like I said in before you will be charged with an extra fee, but if its not complicated and had some extra time I can considered to do it for free, or if you want to hire someone to do the changes, I will test them and accept but I will be no loneger resposible for any issues that may arise from those changes.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class=" btn-services" href="/ServicesP">Dive into Services ðŸŒŠ</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>


<style>

    .container-FAQservices{
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        width: 60%;
    }

    .btn-services{
        display: block;
        width: fit-content;
        margin: 5% auto;
        padding: 10px 30px;
        background-color: #344E41;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

   

</style>